00:00:01.400 --> 00:00:06.500
Welcome to the art of cooking
Today we're gonna make together

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:12.339
The Egyptian dish koshary
Ingredients

00:00:12.339 --> 00:00:13.339
1.

00:00:13.339 --> 00:00:15.949
1 cup brown lentils
2.

00:00:15.949 --> 00:00:18.060
1 cup rice
3.

00:00:18.060 --> 00:00:23.800
1 cup uncooked pasta (small shells or elbow
macaroni is best)

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:24.800
4.

00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:27.540
2 large onions, diced
5.

00:00:27.540 --> 00:00:30.339
4 cloves garlic, minced
6.

00:00:30.339 --> 00:00:32.600
2 tablespoons oil
7.

00:00:32.600 --> 00:00:40.410
1 (400 g) can 
tomatoes juice

00:00:40.410 --> 00:00:41.410
8.

00:00:41.410 --> 00:00:47.110
1/4 teaspoon crushed red chili pepper flakes
(or more to taste)

00:00:47.110 --> 00:00:48.180
9.

00:00:48.180 --> 00:00:51.780
salt and black pepper
the procedures

00:00:51.780 --> 00:00:54.090
1.

00:00:54.090 --> 00:00:57.860
Cook the lentils in just over a liter of salted
water.

00:00:57.860 --> 00:00:59.100
2.

00:00:59.100 --> 00:01:06.220
Bring to a boil, reduce the heat and simmer,
covered, for 15-30 minutes, depending on the

00:01:06.220 --> 00:01:09.510
type of lentils you are using.

00:01:09.510 --> 00:01:10.630
3.

00:01:10.630 --> 00:01:15.490
When the lentils are quite tender, add the
rice to the lentils and continue simmering

00:01:15.490 --> 00:01:19.720
until the rice is cooked, adding water if
necessary.

00:01:19.720 --> 00:01:20.910
4.

00:01:20.910 --> 00:01:23.800
Cook the macaroni in a separate pot.

00:01:23.800 --> 00:01:24.930
5.

00:01:24.930 --> 00:01:27.800
Rinse and strain when done.

00:01:27.800 --> 00:01:28.800
6.

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:33.340
Meanwhile, fry the onions and garlic in the
oil until golden.

00:01:33.340 --> 00:01:34.630
7.

00:01:34.630 --> 00:01:42.220
Add the tomatoes, chilli flakes, salt and
pepper to taste and let it bubble for 10-20

00:01:42.220 --> 00:01:46.270
minutes or until thickened and sauce like.

00:01:46.270 --> 00:01:48.150
8.

00:01:48.150 --> 00:01:56.350
You can now blitz the sauce in a food processor
until smooth or just leave as is.

00:01:56.350 --> 00:01:57.880
9.

00:01:57.880 --> 00:02:01.890
Mix the lentils, rice and macaroni together
in one pot.

00:02:01.890 --> 00:02:03.020
10.

00:02:03.020 --> 00:02:09.060
Place some of the lentil mixture on each plate
and top with tomato sauce.

00:02:09.060 --> 00:02:10.289
11.

00:02:10.289 --> 00:02:16.500
Sprinkle with more hot chili powder or salt
and pepper, if desired.

00:02:16.500 --> 00:02:21.400
and that's how koshary is being sold in egypt

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:25.060
now you're ready for your delicious koshary

